an><br />\n<a href=\"https://kbfl-campaign.github.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbfl-campaign.github.io&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=c2ca06b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kbfl-campaign.github.io</a><br />\n直接網上填表唔洗寄3分鐘搞掂<br />\n[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=f43ee131\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=28b0abf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=06baed4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用email/fax交 今晚1200截</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=8b624c6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]2019選民登記 推爆佢 7月2號截止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"d13ee616739776661a0a0fe242f4919a9056ead5","tid":1279192,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"消防架船有份係71升旗噴水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0a51a64580ce9da68a550b84a0ead63c36bceb","tid":1279192,"uid":38358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d13ee616739776661a0a0fe242f4919a9056ead5","tid":1279192,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"消防架船有份係71升旗噴水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"佢地冇得say no 的"},{"pid":"8ad8b10bb915362be49a23bd81912c1c1c873aab","tid":1279192,"uid":6910,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"71零晨做完火燭 返緊局 咁啱俾人封咗路 <br />\n果下好想同你地講句 小心 加油"},{"pid":"2d6cd89b169867fbc6cb2487d1017734be1794f0","tid":1279192,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ad8b10bb915362be49a23bd81912c1c1c873aab","tid":1279192,"uid":6910,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"71零晨做完火燭 返緊局 咁啱俾人封咗路 <br />\n果下好想同你地講句 小心 加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:03:07.0